{
  "stem": "18474.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what the future would hold, but-- you now, but as of that time, wasn't much change.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we still lived approximately the same way, but they started to-- like the mill became already government property.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't-- they took it away from the owner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The big stuff, the big enterprises, right away became government.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were a little, you know, so in time probably it would have changed for us, too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pretty much the same, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The next change was when the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1941, June 1941.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The war start-- the war started in June, June the 20th, and within-- that was on a Sunday morning.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- and the Germans came to us I remember Thursday or Friday they were already there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It took them only four days or five days, we were occupied by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we seen a lot of Russians running away and-- and as far as us Jews, right away, we knew we were in trouble.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Right away they took away the horses, the cows, everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we never thought they're going to take our lives away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we were wrong.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] --within a few days, we heard they'd shot two boys.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were walking somewhere, they got killed by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The rabbi was taken away eight or 10 days later, picked up and never came back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Till today we don't know what happened to him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And a few more prominent people from the time, they disappeared.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "With the help of the Ukrainians, they took a big part in our lives because they knew everybody, they knew who was what and who was-- who was Jewish and who was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the-- they did a-- they did a good job.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
